{"tid":571414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新春金多寶得主另有其人　水警總部洗碗女工遭誤會中獎","createTime":"2018-02-24T15:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T16:07:27.000Z","uid":89595,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7f618b91e7c3f69f35dd840c3f4517fb56583c73","tid":571414,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"一名女士手持一張六合彩中獎的支票的照片在網上瘋傳，獎金價值逾6600萬，亦盛傳該女士為水警基地餐廳的一名女工。據了解，消息在警隊內部流傳後，有內部人員晚上向餐廳求證，證實有關為誤傳，只是餐廳有一名洗碗女工的身形外貌與相中人相似，因此被同事誤會中獎。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180224/s00001/1519486454855\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180224%2Fs00001%2F1519486454855&d=HfNrgXPymsOIlUf6%2B%2FTneP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=fb9010db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180224%2Fs00001%2F1519486454855&h=825b2178\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180224/s00001/1519486454855</a>"},{"pid":"9746cadd8dabd36341356a588059763aedbd1a40","tid":571414,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T15:38:52.000Z","msg":"又炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb733ec755e40953497b379b229ee50c7c219fd","tid":571414,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T15:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4456b94b6dc83872bd11303e645bd50b452c5a7a","tid":571414,"uid":13257,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T15:39:42.000Z","msg":"係咪見太高調，縮沙了"},{"pid":"7a253951e46375054941f2070d45216cc155ad22","tid":571414,"uid":69886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T15:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.